00:00:55.470 --> 00:00:57.530
This is what bacteria
use to reproduce. 

00:00:57.530 --> 00:01:00.910
There's budding, where a large organism
creates a little bud on its surface 

00:01:00.910 --> 00:01:03.580
with the correct genetic material
