vegetative reproduction, 

00:01:07.900 --> 00:01:09.680
where you take a
cutting from a plant, 

00:01:09.680 --> 00:01:10.900
plant that cutting
in the ground, 

00:01:10.900 --> 00:01:12.850
and let it grow into
its own organisms.

00:01:12.850 --> 00:01:14.550
Sexual reproduction,
